# {{ project_name }}

A Stillsite project. Common commands:

```bash
cms seed       # starter content (fictional, all languages)
cms validate   # rules; non-zero exit on errors
cms build      # deterministic build into _site/
cms export --target swa   # or nginx | generic
cms preview
```

- Put media files under `media/` and reference them by relative path.
- Override any theme template or asset under `theme/templates` and
  `theme/assets` without forking the theme.
